{"tid":2316762,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IZ*ONE 回歸啦！〈One-reeler / Act IV〉實體唱片、數位音源都奪冠","createTime":"2020-12-08T05:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T07:38:11.000Z","uid":16659,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d4d50225af2da61bc53660d10be8e0c94722f5","tid":2316762,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_b50dc8a9de43f5c90a0f34e7b471ceb7/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-08/132163-888018.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_b50dc8a9de43f5c90a0f34e7b471ceb7%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-08%2F132163-888018.png&h=d56e5aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIZ*ONE 從出道以來每次發片都有好成績，昨晚問世的〈One-reeler / Act IV〉當然也不例外！<br />\n<br />\nIZ*ONE 昨晚（7 日）發行第四張迷你專輯〈One-reeler / Act IV〉後，隨後便因為在發行當天賣出 19 萬張，立刻登上 Hanteo Chart 的即時專輯銷量榜冠軍寶座。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_42d77497fca12fba8d81839ac0d55bd4/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-08/132163-888017.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_42d77497fca12fba8d81839ac0d55bd4%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-08%2F132163-888017.jpeg&h=8c24484b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在這同時，最新主打歌 &ldquo;Panorama&rdquo; 也同樣獲得了好成績。以今天上午的數據為準，&ldquo;Panorama&rdquo; 在 Bugs 和 Genie 即時榜上都獲得第一名，在 VIBE 的國內急速上升榜、MelOn 即時榜上也名列前茅。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，最近 IZ*ONE 除了登上《2020 MAMA》搶先公開表演新歌，昨天也在回歸秀上帶來精彩的表演！<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：Off the Record、Mnet）"},{"pid":"b668c63041763cb0f2ba42d0124850a5a0134b95","tid":2316762,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc242cb06ce3baefc837bc913f67af80e81ffa4d","tid":2316762,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,